{"id": "1415972606871339058", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：神明诞生之日，今日发布～欢迎大家收听、下载及分享～如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日\n她与祂，不可共存，于是一柄匕首刺入两颗心脏，那是她向神明奉上的报偿。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Day of Divine Parturition\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\nMorimens OST: \"Day of Divine Parturition\" \nShe and It could not coexist. With a dagger, she drove her no into their twin hearts, an answer etched in blood.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:09:36.977000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 15}, {"emoji": "drool", "emoji_id": "1356053063139463248", "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1415972607295098912", "filename": "5f393e47cfa67b48.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1890855, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972607295098912/5f393e47cfa67b48.jpg?ex=69ccd2c1&is=69cb8141&hm=a19330011560db07c4ad3589ffc19f1a3ab9802636fd137dbe3cd7499b1d71d2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415972742616059975", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.纯白神女-Blessed Maiden-**\n\n神迹若有形状，应如她合十的双手。\n神明若有样貌，应如她安宁的面庞。\n\nIf miracles had a shape, they would be the curve of her fingers clasped in prayer.\nIf the divine ever wore a face, it would be hers: serene as a still lake to drown in.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:10:09.341000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1415972741936316516", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1220508, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972741936316516/1.jpg?ex=69ccd2e1&is=69cb8161&hm=8fb5a3385a20d2b2d5a55a1e2a6c84c7c066ee95b61a18cc404cd2758eec12f3&"}, {"id": "1415972742313934912", "filename": "1-Blessed_Maiden-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1302821, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972742313934912/1-Blessed_Maiden-.mp3?ex=69ccd2e1&is=69cb8161&hm=c5bc882b285573b25c9e797349fee7b77604cefdc2ad19a5fe4116cda1174f7e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415972862015045703", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.偿还-Due Debt-**\n\n他记得她。\n那个在风暴中被自己紧紧抱于襁褓中的孩子，最终被自己亲手送往了深渊——用以与自己的良心一起，交换那个白鸟翱翔的梦境。\n他祈盼一生的美梦已经实现，接下来，是时候该用余下的生命，去偿还所有漆黑的罪孽。\n\nHe remembers her.\nThe child he cradled in the storm, the one he gave to the Abyss—along with his conscience—in exchange for his dream of a homeland where white birds soar.\nNow the dream is real.\nNow the debt comes due.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:10:37.808000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1415972860505362472", "filename": "2-Due_Debt-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1936447, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972860505362472/2-Due_Debt-.mp3?ex=69ccd2fd&is=69cb817d&hm=150e8b43230cd27ed1d004b2876d12ea2166cb14d0365bbd2c749482054c7129&"}, {"id": "1415972861281177661", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1196173, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972861281177661/2.jpg?ex=69ccd2fd&is=69cb817d&hm=2006685ddb493306d004bbf2e06278db51169501aac8d339d78e60378e511b7e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415972991472242719", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.倒错的星辰-Twisted Stars-**\n\n星星只是如常运转在它的轨道，而尘埃中的生命已因此几经沉沦。\n\nThe stars do not care. They keep their indifferent orbits, while the lives below crumble to dust, rise, and crumble again.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:11:08.673000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1415972990826450995", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1238196, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972990826450995/3.jpg?ex=69ccd31c&is=69cb819c&hm=18ec0be5a6b76a6c2d1857c63faad1b2d3bd28f9354fe16140732bb908bf66ee&"}, {"id": "1415972991149277316", "filename": "3-Twisted_Stars-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 3753316, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415972991149277316/3-Twisted_Stars-.mp3?ex=69ccd31c&is=69cb819c&hm=c4be5d735110987ed74f2d5c86d10f0edd8b118e09d11d942e1f41f011101c5b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415973105842782238", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.冷月光-Cold Moonlight-**\n\n月光下的祭祀刀闪烁着诱人的光亮。\n她用一场决绝的死亡，证明了她梦寐以求的自由意志。\n\nThe Sacrificial Knife glimmers, hungry, under the moon.\nShe presses it to her own throat, not in surrender, but to prove her free will with the only way she knows.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:11:35.941000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1415973103921791136", "filename": "4-Cold_Moonlight-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 3656350, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973103921791136/4-Cold_Moonlight-.mp3?ex=69ccd337&is=69cb81b7&hm=c2e43697ffad9fa4676e2d9a0ff334c03d2e0ee48d225229d3183a32420d3e74&"}, {"id": "1415973104685158432", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1208664, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973104685158432/4.jpg?ex=69ccd337&is=69cb81b7&hm=dc9ead43e7f9d67e659e197e9dc52ca6e031df2f1be4531fde2ffd088a5f3ff3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415973215427235962", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.第一餐-First Feeding-**\n\n咔嚓、咔嚓。\n神明咧开嘴巴，欣然收下了信徒所有的虔诚，以及信徒本身。\n\nCrunch, crunch.\nThe newborn god grins, hungrily savoring Its believers' devotion, along with the believers themselves.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:12:02.068000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1415973214487576647", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1216191, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973214487576647/5.jpg?ex=69ccd351&is=69cb81d1&hm=52ad9d71e254bb4834f73c49082fa8e7ffeb700c7f712abe26f45e257fb96207&"}, {"id": "1415973214907273327", "filename": "5-First_Feeding-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1121845, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973214907273327/5-First_Feeding-.mp3?ex=69ccd351&is=69cb81d1&hm=34c8776cfc18d6b8868a37a5ffc1d6e2ebbc4ac5419f1ced367c3e5879edd0fd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415973331353469101", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06.神明降诞-Birth of a God-**\n\n孩子哭闹、尖啼、蛮不讲理。\n祂即宇宙之中心，祂即此地一切法。\n祂要一切目光所及的，都围绕、依从、敬献于祂。\n\nThe infant screams, demands, rages.\nIt is the center of the universe. It is the statute of all becomings.\nAll within Its sight must serve, obey, or be consumed.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:12:29.707000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1415973329730535487", "filename": "6-Birth_of_a_God-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 5967664, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973329730535487/6-Birth_of_a_God-.mp3?ex=69ccd36d&is=69cb81ed&hm=597fbe217eed0f8dda9246906c86a99158ad3d0432351ca514d6fce33ee1b2fd&"}, {"id": "1415973330502291486", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1228008, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973330502291486/6.jpg?ex=69ccd36d&is=69cb81ed&hm=e7a52605181274c105bbea186e54b2483b1cf582ed20d46aab3c8bbf81e46204&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1415973436487893052", "channel_id": "1415972606871339058", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07.白鸟之乡-Homeland-**\n\n转身离开的那一刻，埃尔顿仿佛又变成了那个刚刚出海的少年，蓝天与一望无际的大海连接在一起，世界大得足够装下所有抱负与美梦。\n不一样的是，这次他已清楚地见过了美梦实现的样子，并拥有了一条通往那满是白鸟的、梦乡的归途。\n\nWhen Elton turns his back and leaves, for a moment, he is that boy again, staring at the horizon where sky meets the vast blue sea, a world big enough for every dream to come true.\nBut now he knows the shape of dreams fulfilled. Now he carries a map back to that land of white birds.", "timestamp": "2025-09-12T08:12:54.773000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1415973435682717697", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1213481, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973435682717697/7.jpg?ex=69ccd386&is=69cb8206&hm=a5bcffa64d2a9dcac601a1fcc6e2e8b373171cb35c7a8f98b791f2d23fe7df8a&"}, {"id": "1415973436072919057", "filename": "7-Homeland-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 2559625, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415972606871339058/1415973436072919057/7-Homeland-.mp3?ex=69ccd386&is=69cb8206&hm=e56eb3b86ca1b27b6e1de7ef7408380757e76fdbbdf803b225b4417e43f866f5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415972606871339058", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：神明诞生之日", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
